Problem Definition{panel}
Currently, there's no way to add more than one Identity Provider Entity ID in Atlassian Access's SAML configuration.
 This turns IdP initiated logins impossible for more than one instance since most Identity Providers don't have the possibility to use the same Entity ID in more than one App on the provider side.
h3. Suggested Solution

Add the ability to set multiple Identity Providers Entity IDs so that customers can set multiple apps at the Provider side, one for each of their instances.
